<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFFlora_K.2C_Hahn_M.2C_Rosen_H.2C_Benner_K1998">Flora K, Hahn M, Rosen H, Benner K (1998). "Milk thistle (Silybum marianum) for the therapy of liver disease". <i>Am. J. Gastroenterol.</i> <b>93</b> (2): 139–43. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1572-0241.1998.00139.x" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1572-0241.1998.00139.x" rel="nofollow">10.1111/j.1572-0241.1998.00139.x</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9468229" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9468229">PMID 9468229</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Milk+thistle+%28Silybum+marianum%29+for+the+therapy+of+liver+disease&amp;rft.jtitle=Am.+J.+Gastroenterol.&amp;rft.aulast=Flora+K%2C+Hahn+M%2C+Rosen+H%2C+Benner+K&amp;rft.au=Flora+K%2C+Hahn+M%2C+Rosen+H%2C+Benner+K&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.volume=93&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=139%E2%80%9343&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1111%2Fj.1572-0241.1998.00139.x&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/9468229&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Milk_thistle"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
